---
title: Chili-Loaded Sweet Potatoes with Monterey Jack and Hot Sauce Crema
description: To take our chili to the next level, we spiked it with zesty long green pepper, umami’d it up with stock concentrate, and sprinkled in our signature Southwest spice blend. As if that weren’t crazy enough, we piled it all atop split baked sweet potatoes and whipped up a hot sauce crema for dolloping over.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5cc2016a427b1c00094e8386-ed79f1e7.jpg
